latestPosts.caption:
WE’RE MOVING INTO A BIGGER FACTORY!!! 🏭🍫

We’ve been quiet lately… online but def not offline 👀

It’s been all hands on deck, packing boxes, hauling machines, and saying goodbye to the lil’ space that started it all 🥹💛

This move is a huge milestone for us. The upgraded factory has been nearly a year in the making… and it’s finally HERE!!!

More space = more capacity, more creativity, and more of the chocolate snacks you love (plus way more room to dance between batches 💃🕺)

Thank you for snacking with us 💫 can’t wait to show you what’s next!!!

POCKET’S 🍫 IS NOW IN @WHOLEFOODS!!!!! 🥳🥳🥳

Pocket’s Fam!!! Your favorite chocolate almonds have now landed in all @wholefoods locations across SOCAL, ARIZONA, NEVADA, & HAWAII 🏝️🏜️🌵🌺🛒 AHHHH!!!!

Hit up our store locator and run to the nearest Whole Foods to come celebrate with us 🎉🎉🎉 Grab a bag or if you’re feeling nuts like we are, clear the WHOLE shelf!!!!! 💨

You’ll very likely spot our ‘lil team in the aisles, dancing 💃🏻 jumping 🤸🏻‍♀️ and yapping non-stop about how insanely delicious our Pocket’s almonds are 🎤💥 

Join the party, snap a shelfie and tag us 📸 We’re adding all of your cute pics to our office photo wall so we can look back 20 years from now and be like “REMEMBER WHEN POCKET’S HIT WHOLE FOODS SHELVES FOR THE FIRST TIME AND OUR HEARTS EXPLODED?!?!?! 🥹”
